# .worktreeinclude — files waft should copy from the main worktree into
# linked worktrees. Same syntax as .gitignore. See README.md.
#
# Keep this list small and intentional: every match is a file we want
# carried across when a contributor runs `git worktree add` (and the
# post-checkout hook fires waft). Files outside this list stay behind.

# Local environment overrides (per-developer secrets, direnv config).
.env
.env.*
.envrc
